{"tid":11423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［PlugDJ］屬於巴絲打播歌既音樂台 上線啦！","createTime":"2016-11-29T09:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T13:27:54.000Z","uid":32021,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8aafe4d70c5488a59a879c56a70a698d6119ea33","tid":11423,"uid":32021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T09:40:22.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><em>歡迎大家入&amp;#22175;<span style=\"color: orange;\">PlugHKG</span>分享你鍾意&amp;#22021;歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://plug.dj/hkgolden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplug.dj%2Fhkgolden&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8bc89b33\" target=\"_blank\">https://plug.dj/hkgolden</a></em></strong></span></div><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">關於高登音樂台</span></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3P4Mu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3P4Mu.png&h=cc321a15&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n高登音樂台(PlugHKG) 係由黃犀利巴打係2013年10月建立&amp;#22021;一個基於PlugDJ 音樂分享平台&amp;#22021;&amp;#22050;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至今已經發展&amp;#21655;三年多&amp;#21874;&amp;#22021;時間，係呢兩年裡面我&amp;#21707;亦都抱住為巴絲打帶來 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><em>歡迎大家入&amp;#22175;分享你鍾意&amp;#22021;歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://plug.dj/hkgolden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplug.dj%2Fhkgolden&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8bc89b33\" target=\"_blank\">https://plug.dj/hkgolden</a></em></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家咁鍾意聽歌，有無諗過可以同幾十人一齊係網上面聽你首歌呢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早在2013 年10月我&amp;#21707;就已經係 plug.dj 開辦&amp;#21655;高登音樂台呢個平台<br />\n2014年我&amp;#21707;領先plug.dj 官方首先開發&amp;#21655;專屬流動應用程式及流動版Chatroom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2015年我&amp;#21707;仲自創&amp;#21655;娛樂系統，係入面玩大細，抽獎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然2015年plugdj 服務中斷&amp;#21655;，直到而家上面兩個系統我&amp;#21707;都未重新啟用得返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過2016 年plugdj終於返返&amp;#22175; <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我&amp;#21707;亦第一時間進駐返 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目的就係比大家入&amp;#22175;開開心心播歌識朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無錯，巴絲打專屬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我&amp;#21707;仲設有自己寫&amp;#22021;高登icon 插件添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/28H6wZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F28H6wZ.png&h=3a64f09d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nChrome 安裝教學：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/uRekMORk5qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FuRekMORk5qg&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=591bd9a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/uRekMORk5qg</a><br />\n<br />\nFirefox 安裝教學：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DFkg4FczSRs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDFkg4FczSRs&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=0bbdbc5d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DFkg4FczSRs</a><br />\n<br />\n點樣加歌落去播？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ksmg_biNmIk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dksmg_biNmIk&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=46f2a8d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ksmg_biNmIk</a><br />\n<br />\n想再增強plugdj&amp;#22021;功能？<br />\n可以安裝 RCS ， 一隻外國開發&amp;#22021;插件 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://rcs.radiant.dj/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frcs.radiant.dj%2F&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=070c3f65\" target=\"_blank\">https://rcs.radiant.dj/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">食屎啦 林早洩！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">暫時只支援電腦</span></span>"},{"pid":"699e25df4aa9dce2fce54c02dad0cf53751264e2","tid":11423,"uid":32021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>&lt;em&gt;歡迎大家入嚟<span style=\"color: orange;\">PlugHKG</span>分享你鍾意嘅歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://plug.dj/hkgolden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplug.dj%2Fhkgolden&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8bc89b33\" target=\"_blank\">https://plug.dj/hkgolden</a>&lt;/em&gt;</strong></span></div><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">關於高登音樂台</span></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://na.cx/i/3P4Mu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3P4Mu.png&h=c41c53c5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n高登音樂台(PlugHKG) 係由黃犀利巴打係2013年10月建立嘅一個基於PlugDJ 音樂分享平台<br />\n至今已經發展咗三年多，係呢兩年裡面我哋亦都抱住為巴絲打帶來 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>&lt;em&gt;歡迎大家入嚟分享你鍾意嘅歌！<br />\n<a href=\"https://plug.dj/hkgolden\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplug.dj%2Fhkgolden&d=BbGirfR5U81eMP64OYU5HGN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=8bc89b33\" target=\"_blank\">https://plug.dj/hkgolden</a>&lt;/em&gt;</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n大家咁鍾意聽歌，有無諗過可以同幾十人一齊係網上面聽你首歌呢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\